<idx><h>AWT</h></idx>
<idx><h>java.awt</h></idx>
The Java library includes the package <c>java.awt</c> for drawing 2D graphics.
<em>AWT</em> stands for <q>Abstract Window Toolkit</q>.
We are only going to scratch the surface of graphics programming.
You can read more about it in the Java tutorials (see \url{https://thinkjava.org/java2d}).
</p>
